        an artist’s project to finance their upcoming hits,
        music videos and other costs.</p>

      </div>

      <div class="home-features-feature col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12">

        <%= image_tag("home-feature-3.svg")%>
        <h3>Become rich</h3>
